{
  "text": "That's what I thought you'd say. Now we get back to the business at hand of doing the book. I want, as we cover this early part of the 75,000 year cycle, I would like to go back a little bit, quite some distance, perhaps, before the 75,000 years occurred and take one more look at the transfer of entities from Walbeck to clear up this point. I'd like to check the uh uh time that you gave us because we had some distortions in numbers back in the early part of this, and I'm afraid this might be a distorted. These entities from MALDEC were transferred how many years ago? I am Ra the Entities of which you speak underwent several transitions, the first occurring a five, a zero, a zero, a thousand of your years approximately in your past as you measure time. At this time the entities were transformed into a not. This continued for what you would call eons of your time. Those aiding them were repeatedly unable to reach them at a period approximately a two zero zero thousand years in your past as you measure time. A confederation entity was able to begin to relax this knot from which nun had escaped during a planetary annihilation. These entities then were transformed again into the inner or time space dimensions, and underwent a lengthy process of healing. When this was accomplished, these entities were then able to determine the appropriate movement, shall we say, in order to set up conditions for alleviation of the consequences of their actions at a time four, six zero zero zero forty six thousand of your years in your past as you measure time. This being approximate of these entities chose incarnation within the planetary sphere.",
